&kp TAB  &kp Z  &kp X  &kp C     &kp V            &kp B             &kp N            &kp M        &kp COMMA            &kp DOT  &kp FSLH       &kp RIGHT_BRACKET
                       &sk LGUI  &lt 1 BACKSPACE  &kp LEFT_SHIFT    &mt LCTRL ENTER  &lt 2 SPACE  &mt LEFT_ALT ESCAPE
